6. Post the PR URL as a comment on the merge spark and mark the spark completed:
`ryve comment add ryve-1c5beea9 '<pr-url>'`
`ryve spark close ryve-1c5beea9 completed`
7. Exit. Do **not** merge to main automatically — human review is required.

